    f_values = [0] * (n // 2 + 1)
    h_values = [0] * (n // 1 + 1)
    ans = 0
    n //= 2
    for i in range(1, n + 1):
        h_values[i] = n // i - 1
    for i in range(1, n + 1):
        f_values[i] = i * (i - 1) // 2
        j = 2
        while i * j <= n:
            f_values[i] -= f_values[i * j]
            j += 1
        ans = (ans + i * f_values[i]) % MOD
    return ans * 2 % MOD
